Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.41,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}無論從哪個角度去看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:36.79,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}世界都很廣闊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:43.22,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}沒有見過的事物  想要去找到
